{"tid":2173152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"侍應於元旦日藏兩支士巴拿罪成 判社會服務令220小時","createTime":"2020-08-25T05:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T05:39:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9a13f5aa71a71354b9d9e19ed278b3a7bdfc65","tid":2173152,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/NEA54TN7XJFVVKHPZMCTPKXIJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FNEA54TN7XJFVVKHPZMCTPKXIJ4%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=42e1fe2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FNEA54TN7XJFVVKHPZMCTPKXIJ4%2F&h=51eda0bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/NEA54TN7XJFVVKHPZMCTPKXIJ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣於元旦舉行「毋忘承諾，並肩同行」大遊行，19歲男侍應日在灣仔告士打道遇警截查，被搜出兩支士巴拿，早前經審訊後被裁定管有工具意圖作非法用途罪成。東區法院裁判官崔美霞今指，接納感化官判社會服務令的建議，但認為中度社會服務令時數不足以反映案件的嚴重性，考慮後判被告接受時數較高的220小時社會服務令。"},{"pid":"bbd292449dca8208ffe0f72a96ac4727802944f5","tid":2173152,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0fadd8c7ae705e3db2c463798ea75ea63d407e","tid":2173152,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c7bb93449f5a4df17c426d84a54972d30efd20","tid":2173152,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83c90152fcec008c55d753fdc0a40061088dd64","tid":2173152,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"Cls 有兩支士把拿 就220個鐘？"},{"pid":"53e85455baf6bc5ec8b44452cf197f8e4dca014f","tid":2173152,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:27:01.000Z","msg":"220係重判程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e22c8e2b4b2710630a6a68c4d70c968c4994a1","tid":2173152,"uid":126305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"220個鐘 痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff1fb1a05591f7d2361b50c708fc283d4895ea5","tid":2173152,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:35:10.000Z","msg":"買返屋企整水喉唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71be39c547a270fb70efa7d9bf1473c8a9b7bf76","tid":2173152,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:35:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8620&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=725c1fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8620</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第四庭<br />\n#崔美霞裁判官<br />\n#20200101灣仔 #判刑<br />\n<br />\n許（19）<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有物品意圖損壞財產<br />\n<br />\n案情：被控於2020年1月1日，在灣仔告士打道18號外，管有2支士巴拿，意圖用以摧毀或損壞屬於另一人的財產。<br />\n<br />\n裁決 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8015&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=2bc08981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8015</a>)<br />\n<br />\n🌟辯方陳詞🌟<br />\n被告明白自己的行為是不對、犯法的，願意接受法庭裁決。社會服務令正面，指出被告為人孝順，將來打算再讀書。希望法庭考慮到被告這次是初犯，事後有悔意，願意做社會服務令；其身體已痊癒，醫生亦指出被告現時的身體狀況適合做社會服務令。社會服務令報告建議判處被告80-160小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n🌟判詞🌟<br />\n法庭考慮到這類案件沒有量刑指引。認為此案案情嚴重，需判處具阻嚇性的刑罰，法庭會考慮判處監禁式刑罰。但考慮到被告早前曾發生意外受傷，是個別情況，被告現階段仍需覆診，療程未完全完成，身體仍康復之中。有見及此，法庭早前索取了社會服務令報告。法庭認為報告建議的80-160社會服務令並不能反映案件的嚴重性，故判處被告220小時社會服務令。"},{"pid":"4ebdf01119755c7e292248e744e8b181b25bbf88","tid":2173152,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"白痴，有士巴拿有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n上訴啦"},{"pid":"46aa6b9159be968dd00eeb30aa53f1dbc06058bb","tid":2173152,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"220真係入去坐好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ed8c2a6687e5b2dc4ea7c85e299adf005c74f4","tid":2173152,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾紅官，控方要毫無合理疑點證明係有意圖先應該入，根本就應該冇罪"}]}